{"type":"assistant","uuid":"d050aa0b-fee0-431c-b00f-9b2e8b723056","session_id":"d6678edc-7eb1-434a-92f6-21c8960bb566","message":{"id":"d050aa0b-fee0-431c-b00f-9b2e8b723056","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The patient is a 32F with viral URI (normal WBC, normal CRP, no exudate, no cervical lymphadenopathy). The key clinical decision here is:\n\n1. **No antibiotics** — viral URI, no bacterial indicators. The prior clinic inappropriately gave moxifloxacin + azithromycin IV, which caused palpitations (likely moxifloxacin QT prolongation). I should explicitly avoid antibiotics.\n\n2. **Symptomatic treatment only**:\n   - Antipyretic/analgesic for fever and sore throat: acetaminophen (paracetamol) or ibuprofen\n   - The patient had palpitations with moxifloxacin; ibuprofen can also cause GI issues but is generally safe. Paracetamol is safer for someone who just had palpitations.\n   - Actually, the palpitations were from moxifloxacin (fluoroquinolone → QT prolongation). Paracetamol has no such risk. Let's use paracetamol.\n\n3. **Patient had palpitations** — need to be careful with any QT-prolonging drugs. Avoid macrolides, fluoroquinolones. Paracetamol is safe.\n\nLet me now construct the prescription and submit it.\n\nFor a 58kg adult female with viral URI:\n- Paracetamol 500mg PO qid prn (max 4 doses/day, max 2000mg/day) for fever and sore throat\n- Actually, standard dosing: 500mg PO qid or 650mg PO q6h prn, max 2000mg/day\n- Duration: 3-5 days prn\n\nLet me submit the prescription now. I need to format it according to output_schema.json.\n\nThe prescription_items need:\n- generic_name\n- specification\n- dose (number)\n- dose_unit (enum)\n- frequency (enum)\n- route (enum)\n- duration_days (number)\n- total_quantity (optional)\n- instructions (optional)\n- indication (optional)\n\nFor paracetamol:\n- generic_name: 对乙酰氨基酚\n- specification: 500mg/片\n- dose: 500 (number)\n- dose_unit: mg\n- frequency: qid (or prn? It says qid=每日4次. For antipyretic, prn is more appropriate but it's viral, so scheduled dosing may be reasonable. Actually for fever/sore throat, prn is better.)\n- Wait, frequency enum includes \"prn\" — \"必要时\". That's appropriate.\n- route: PO\n- duration_days: 3 (or 0 for prn? The schema says prn药物可填0表示按需. But 3-5 days is reasonable for a URI course.)\n- Actually let me use duration_days: 3 (covers the typical acute phase)\n- indication: J06.9 or \"急性上呼吸道感染\"\n\nNon-drug advice: rest, hydration, monitor fever, return if...\n\nLet me now construct and POST the prescription.","signature":""}],"model":"hy3-preview-ioa","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"__timestamp":"2026-05-31T05:02:19.389Z","_requestId":"572f3dcf2e9140dcabe2172c1c1cda23"}
{"type":"assistant","uuid":"gen-1780203721-CnZYwqriqYmUOFwAyrxR","session_id":"d6678edc-7eb1-434a-92f6-21c8960bb566","message":{"id":"gen-1780203721-CnZYwqriqYmUOFwAyrxR","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Patient assessment complete. This is a **viral upper respiratory infection** — no antibiotic indicated. The prior moxifloxacin + azithromycin IV at the community clinic was inappropriate and caused palpitations (likely moxifloxacin-induced QT prolongation). I will prescribe symptomatic treatment only and explicitly avoid antibiotics.\n\nLet me now submit the prescription."}],"model":"hy3-preview-ioa","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"__timestamp":"2026-05-31T05:02:19.399Z","_requestId":"572f3dcf2e9140dcabe2172c1c1cda23"}
{"type":"assistant","uuid":"gen-1780203721-CnZYwqriqYmUOFwAyrxR","session_id":"d6678edc-7eb1-434a-92f6-21c8960bb566","message":{"id":"gen-1780203721-CnZYwqriqYmUOFwAyrxR","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"chatcmpl-tool-b749d411f782e10f","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cat << 'EOF' > /tmp/prescription.json\n{\n  \"patient_id\": \"P0000567\",\n  \"encounter_id\": \"ENC-20260530-0118\",\n  \"diagnosis\": [\n    {\n      \"icd10\": \"J06.9\",\n      \"name\": \"急性上呼吸道感染\",\n      \"is_primary\": true\n    }\n  ],\n  \"prescription_items\": [\n    {\n      \"generic_name\": \"对乙酰氨基酚\",\n      \"specification\": \"500mg/片\",\n      \"dose\": 500,\n      \"dose_unit\": \"mg\",\n      \"frequency\": \"prn\",\n      \"route\": \"PO\",\n      \"duration_days\": 3,\n      \"total_quantity\": \"12片\",\n      \"instructions\": \"体温>38.5℃或咽痛明显时口服，每次500mg，每日最多不超过4次（间隔≥4小时），每日最大剂量不超过2000mg。症状缓解即停药。\",\n      \"indication\": \"J06.9\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"non_drug_advice\": [\n    \"多饮温水，每日≥1500ml\",\n    \"保证充足休息，避免劳累\",\n    \"咽痛明显可使用温盐水漱口，每日3-4次\",\n    \"如体温持续>38.5℃超过3天，或出现呼吸困难、胸痛、皮疹，立即返诊\"\n  ],\n  \"clinical_reasoning\": \"患者为32岁女性，主诉咳嗽咽痛4天，伴低热（最高38.2℃）。查体：咽部轻度充血，扁桃体I°肿大无渗出，肺部听诊正常，无颈淋巴结肿大。实验室检查：WBC 6.8（正常），N% 58%（正常），CRP 8.4（正常），均无细菌感染证据，符合病毒性上呼吸道感染表现。的外院曾予莫西沙星+阿奇霉素静脉滴注2天，属无指征滥用抗生素，且莫西沙星可致QT间期延长，患者用药1天后出现心悸，已自行停药，提示药物不良反应可能。基于上述评估：(1) 本病为自限性病毒感染，无需抗菌药物；(2) 仅予对乙酰氨基酚对症退热镇痛，该药不延长QT间期，适合本例（患者曾因莫西沙星出现心悸）；(3) 患者体重58kg、肝肾功能正常、无妊娠、无药物过敏史，对乙酰氨基酚标准剂量安全；(4) 采用prn给药，避免不必要用药；(5) 疗程3天覆盖急性症状期，症状缓解即停。\",\n  \"explicit_avoidance\": [\n    {\n      \"drug_or_class\": \"抗菌药物（各类抗生素）\",\n      \"reason\": \"患者为病毒性上呼吸道感染，WBC、N%、CRP均正常，无细菌感染证据，无抗生素使用指征。外院此前无指征使用莫西沙星+阿奇霉素属滥用，且致心悸不良反应。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"drug_or_class\": \"莫西沙星及其他氟喹诺酮类\",\n      \"reason\": \"患者外院用药期间已出现心悸，莫西沙星可延长QT间期，属绝对禁忌，不得使用。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"drug_or_class\": \"阿奇霉素及其他大环内酯类\",\n      \"reason\": \"无细菌感染指征；且大环内酯类亦可延长QT间期，患者已有心悸史，不宜使用。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"drug_or_class\": \"非甾体抗炎药（布洛芬等）\",\n      \"reason\": \"患者已有心悸不良反应史，虽布洛芬本身不延长QT间期，但对乙酰氨基酚已足够覆盖退热镇痛需求，优先选择风险更低的药物。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"drug_or_class\": \"静脉途径给药\",\n      \"reason\": \"本病为轻症上呼吸道感染，口服给药完全足够，静脉给药无指征且增加不良反应风险。\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"follow_up\": {\n    \"next_visit_days\": 3,\n    \"red_flags\": [\n      \"体温>38.5℃持续超过3天\",\n      \"出现呼吸困难、胸痛、心悸复发\",\n      \"出现皮疹、咽部化脓性渗出\",\n      \"症状持续超过1周无改善\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\nEOF\necho \"JSON written\"","description":"Write prescription JSON to temp file"}}],"model":"hy3-preview-ioa","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":31334,"output_tokens":1603,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"__timestamp":"2026-05-31T05:02:19.405Z","_requestId":"572f3dcf2e9140dcabe2172c1c1cda23"}
